# Cloudflare Pages redirects. Netlify-style; read natively by CF Pages.
# Docs: https://developers.cloudflare.com/pages/configuration/redirects/
#
# These rules run before the static asset server, so they override
# whatever Astro emits at the same path.

# Proper 301 for the locale-less root. Astro still generates a
# meta-refresh index.html at / (via `redirects` in astro.config.mjs),
# which keeps local `pnpm dev` useful, but in prod this rule wins and
# sends a real 301 to /en/ — faster and SEO-friendly.
/    /en/    301
